{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"写封信寄给毛主席","authors":["张明权"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":7,"day":30}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写封信寄给毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张明权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起笔来铺开纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写封信寄给毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南来的大雁头上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的信呀赶上去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到我们的邮局里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到我们的火车里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直飞到北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到你的手心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕着我们自己的地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里想起了你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃着我们自己的饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里想起了你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上民校来选干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里想起了你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着遍地好麦苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里想起了你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着槽上新买的牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着才盖的新房子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着门上的红喜对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着刚生的小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里一团火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时三刻想着你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天我们在地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈着你来唱着你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到夜晚我们梦见你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天干活更美气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不完我们的感激意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写不完我们的心头喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不完呀写不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里的千言和万语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“现在春耕已完毕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗已经都出齐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要保证多锄草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要保证多施肥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要起誓保住他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到粮食进囤里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“那怕他今年再生虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕他今年再上水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕他特务想捣乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕他久旱不下雨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕他困难比山大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的信心大百倍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就凭我们一双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产斗争一定能胜利！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月十日  新乡"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}